#pickYourHeroes.helpSlide
  h3
    span(style='color: gray;') 2. 
    | choose your team 
    span(style='font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;color:var(--BACKTOTOP);' onclick="scrollToThisDiv('playGameForward')") [back to top]
  p
    | for games in 
    span(style='color: var(--SERVERCOLOR);') corinth, athens, 
    | and 
    span(style='color: var(--SERVERCOLOR);') sparta, 
    | you can select up to five hero cards. click again on any card you've selected to return it.
  br
  p
    | there are seven available hero classes: 
  ul
    li
      p
        span(style='color:var(--MELEE);') melee
        |  and 
        span(style='color:var(--RANGED);') ranged
        |  fighters tend to have higher 
        span(style='color:var(--STATNAME);') attack
        |  (ATK) and primarily do damage through autoattacks and abilities.        
    li
      p
        span(style='color:var(--SUPPORTER);') supporters
        |  boost allies&apos; stats and bestow various blessings, while 
        span(style='color:var(--CASTER);') casters
        |  impair enemies and worsen enemy stats.
    li
      p
        span(style='color:var(--PROTECTOR);') protectors
        |  often increase the 
        span(style='color:var(--STATNAME);') defense
        |  (DEF) and survivability of allies, while the main purpose of 
        span(style='color: var(--HEALER);') healers
        |  is to restore allies&apos; 
        span(style='color:var(--STATNAME);') health points
        |  (HP).
    li
      p
        span(style='color:var(--SPECIAL);') special
        |  heroes use unique abilities to affect the outcome of the game.
  p
    | if time runs out and you still haven&apos;t picked any heroes, you and your opponent will be returned to the lobby.
